Package: enigma2-plugin-extensions-e2hlsserver
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: madoe21 <https://github.com/madoe21>
Homepage: https://github.com/madoe21/enigma2-hls-server
Source: https://github.com/madoe21/enigma2-hls-server
Section: extra
Priority: optional
Depends: enigma2, ffmpeg
License: MIT
Description: E2 HLS Server for Enigma2
 Streams Enigma2 channels as HLS to any device (Roku, browser, VLC).
 Supports quality profiles (copy, low, medium, high, ultra, custom).
 Uses named pipes for zero-overhead segmentation.
 .
